<div class="cell markdown">
<p>A code fence whose info string names no language opens no code block;
it folds into the paragraph, where its delimiters read as an inline code
span:</p>
<p><code>python {.foo} code</code></p>
<p>Inside such a fold no later line opens a block of its own:</p>
<p><code>not a language # still text, not a heading</code></p>
<p>A fence with no closing fence folds the same way:</p>
<p>``` unterminated</p>
